      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean, \"evolving societal needs\" sounds a lot like just a excuse for judges to do whatever they want politically. isn't there a real danger that if we abandon the original meaning, the constitution just becomes a tool for whoever is in power at the time? it feels pretty much like the law is being replaced by policy preferences.",
